Class ContentWithSize

  • java.lang.Object
    • cscie97.asn2.ecommerce.product.Content
      • cscie97.asn2.ecommerce.product.ContentWithSize

  • public abstract class ContentWithSize
extends Content
    This abstract class is derived from Content and declares content size property. This is inherited by all types of contents which has a size.
